high_descs: Turn right, step forward, turn left and walk to the TV stand.
Pick up the phone to the right of the box.
Turn around and walk to the couch.
Place the phone inside the box.
Pick up the box from the couch.
Turn left, walk forward, then turn right to see a stand underneath a painting.
Place the box to the right of the remote on the stand.
anns.task_desc: Put a phone in a box, place box on a stand.

high_descs: Move so that you're facing the black console table with the tv on it.
Pick up the phone on the right of the box from the table.
With the phone in hand, turn around and cross over to the black couch with the box on it.
Put the phone in the cardboard box on the couch.
Pick up the box from the couch.
Bring the box to your left and go so that you're facing the black end table to the left of the couch.
Put the box down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Move the box with a phone in it to the end table.

high_descs: Move forward to the brown dresser underneath the television.
Pick up the white smartphone to the right of the cardboard box from the top of the dresser.
Turn around and move to the gray couch against the wall.
Place the smartphone in the cardboard box on the couch.
Pick up the cardboard box containing the smartphone from the couch.
Turn left and move to the small brown cabinet to the right of the window and underneath the portrait on the wall.
Place the cardboard box containing the smartphone on top of the cabinet to the right of the remote control.
anns.task_desc: Place a cardboard box containing a smartphone on the cabinet.
